4 rows fetched.

SQL> MERGE INTO products p
  2 USING newproducts np
  3 ON (p.product_id = np.product_id)
  4 WHEN MATCHED THEN
  5   UPDATE SET p.product_name = np.product_name, p.category = np.category WHERE p.product_name != 'play gym'
  6 WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
  7   INSERT VALUES (np.product_id, np.product_name, np.category) WHERE np.category = 'books';

4 rows affected.

